{"tid":2032373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「524」大遊行全攻略！","createTime":"2020-05-24T04:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T08:00:35.000Z","uid":345458,"like":103,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"7adc09fab89a897311bfb2362e00641f6b29c40d","tid":2032373,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:41:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>1. 集合時間/遊行路線</ins></span></span></div></ins></span><br />\n集合時間：1:00pm<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣sogo- -&gt;灣仔修頓球場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FXt7Trt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFXt7Trt.jpg&h=dfe15a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n提醒：今日遊行係一點開始！喺睇到呢個post嘅時候應該係要出咗門口！今日準時好重要！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\">2. 遊行主題－反國歌法</div></ins></span></span><br />\n呢個我都係啱啱先知，因為所有文宣都係咁出。而一個遊行最忌有太多主題，謀體好難focus報。<br />\n<br />\n更何況民陣已經plan緊遊行針對國安法，所以希望大家今次Focus返國歌法！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\">3. 遊行目標－谷人數</div></ins></span></span><br />\n今日目標係谷人數！！向外國證明香港人反惡法嘅決心！所以一點鐘一到，大家就要開始唸辦法聚人，例如搵個冇狗嘅地方開始嗌口號！<br />\n<br />\n今次遊行文宣比上次多咗好多，連登都多咗好多post傾，就連我啲淺黃fd都有喺ig repost今次遊行！人數一定會有一定保證，大家大膽啲聚人！<br />\n<br />\n正因為今次目標係谷人數，大家就真係唔好冒險帶文具啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\">4. 遊行口號</div></ins></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">萬能口號：</span><br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n民族自強，香港獨立！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">針對國歌法口號：</span><br />\n中文嘅可以求其一位手足直接嗌「反國歌法」，之後其他手足跟上。<br />\n<br />\n英文嘅可以試吓「No National Anthem Law！」，嗌法同上面一樣！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Be Water</div></ins></span></span><br />\n大家明嘅<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\">6. 其他</div></ins></span></span><br />\n去唔到記得可以報哨俾fd知！<br />\n<br />\nbtw我好似見唔到今次遊行有公海，如果你認同上面嘅遊行主題...目標等等，可以入呢個公海傾，啱啱開的。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/I-y82BzSTnLamtBGQ2rCuw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FI-y82BzSTnLamtBGQ2rCuw&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtRSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=bac0cb3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/I-y82BzSTnLamtBGQ2rCuw</a>"},{"pid":"fe742885fbe9b2aca3754a471ef765e07c95739d","tid":2032373,"uid":345458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:42:05.000Z","msg":"推到完場"},{"pid":"e68f1e2609cf5cbf3c9fa327873e51caf6abad02","tid":2032373,"uid":345458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"No National Anthem Law<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97fc0fe9bda29927de6fc32ea0f46040215ca739","tid":2032373,"uid":45752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25df0a02be7d5f3163c88f30787c5484dd054705","tid":2032373,"uid":76977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:44:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ed3387ccf9c88191023ea0eb122c6c9be0874ff6","tid":2032373,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752d7d91f3e6a7cc08fa6a3375b2d6b96a80dbb8","tid":2032373,"uid":209391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:45:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"883ad50e57820974b6b7d6a73c6fe91ffacb925e","tid":2032373,"uid":345458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"64616642星火"},{"pid":"15922754e399d09b8ea7d4e58b3fa63ffcf7b123","tid":2032373,"uid":345458,"like":0,"disli